            <title><![CDATA[Bleach: Rebirth of Souls DLC character Retsu Unohana (The Blood Warfare) launches August 18 for Season Pass owners, August 25 for all]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/08/bleach-rebirth-of-souls-dlc-character-retsu-unohana-the-blood-warfare-launches-august-18-for-season-pass-owners-august-25-for-all</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/bleach-rebirth-of-souls-dlc-character-retsu-unohana-the-blood-warfare-launches-august-18-for-season-pass-owners-august-25-for-all.1272759/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PS4</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Second Season Pass character dated.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><em><a title="Games > Bleach: Rebirth of Souls [42 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/bleach-rebirth-of-souls">Bleach: Rebirth of Souls</a></em> downloadable content character Retsu Unohana (The Blood Warfare) will launch on August 18 for Season Pass owners and August 25 for everyone, publisher <a title="Companies > Bandai Namco Entertainment [6,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/bandai-namco-entertainment">Bandai Namco</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Tamsoft [324 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/tamsoft">Tamsoft</a> announced. <span id="more-985015"></span></p><p><em>Bleach: Rebirth of Souls</em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,122 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,694 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,262 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,927 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1689620/BLEACH_Rebirth_of_Souls/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Steam</a>.</p><p>Watch a new trailer below.</p><h2><span>DLC Character Retsu Unohana (The Blood Warfare) Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="BLEACH Rebirth of Souls - Retsu Unohana Reveal Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uv5XQgENZ7c?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="【BLEACH Rebirth of Souls】 DLC第２弾紹介映像｜卯ノ花 烈" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HFdPTy0_aiM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/08/bleach-rebirth-of-souls-dlc-character-retsu-unohana-the-blood-warfare-launches-august-18-for-season-pass-owners-august-25-for-all]]></content:encoded>
