        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Next Tales of remastered project to be announced on August 19]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/08/next-tales-of-remastered-project-to-be-announced-on-august-19</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/next-tales-of-remastered-project-to-be-announced-on-august-19.1272756/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p>The next entry in the “<em><a title="Series > Tales of [10 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/series/tales-of">Tales of</a></em> Remastered Project” series will be announced on <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20250819T1400" target="_blank">August 19 at 7:00 a.m. PT / 10:00 a.m. ET</a>, <a title="Companies > Bandai Namco Entertainment [6,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/bandai-namco-entertainment">Bandai Namco</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/tales_ch/status/1957442544343962055" target="_blank">announced</a>. You will be able to watch it on YouTube (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vky55fYInh8" target="_blank">English</a>, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EfIytHHiIyU" target="_blank">Japanese</a>). <span id="more-985014"></span></p><p>While not yet confirmed by Bandai Namco, a <a href="https://www.resetera.com/threads/bandai-namco-seemingly-accidentally-confirms-tales-of-xillia-remaster-announcement-expected-august-18th.1269954/" target="_blank">leak of the video premiere</a> accidently posted by Bandai Namco last week seems to suggest that <em>Tales of Xillia</em> is the planned announcement.</p><p>The latest remastered title, <em><a title="Games > Tales of Graces f Remastered [5 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/tales-of-graces-f-remastered">Tales of Graces f Remastered</a></em>, launched for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,122 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,694 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,262 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,132 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,518 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,927 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2530980/Tales_of_Graces_f_Remastered/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> on January 17.</p><p><em>Tales of</em> series producer Yusuke Tomizawa has <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2024/12/bandai-namco-to-release-remastered-tales-of-titles-fairly-consistently">previously said</a> Bandai Namco intends to “provide [remastered <em>Tales of</em> titles] fairly consistently,” and “intends to continue doing so as much as possible.”</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/08/next-tales-of-remastered-project-to-be-announced-on-august-19]]></content:encoded>
